### Post market order
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "instrumentId": "{{instrumentId}}",
  "requestId": "{{$guid}}",
  "portfolioId": "{{portfolioId}}",
  "orderDirection": 2, 
  "orderType": 2, 
  "timeInForceType": 0,
  "priceType": 0,
  "price": 0,
  "quantityLots": 10,
  "createdAt": "{{$datetime iso8601}}"
}


